===Etymology===
From {{der|en|frm|benjoin}}, from {{der|en|es|benjuí}}, {{der|en|pt|beijoim}}, {{der|en|it|benzoi}}, from {{der|en|ar|لُبَان جَاوِيّ||Javanese frankincense}}. The initial ''lu'' was probably lost because it was taken as the definite article in Romance. Compare {{m|en|oliban}}.

